1. Create a function that accepts email and password, signup or login
    * This function accepts three parameters, email, password, signup or login
    * Some logic if required here
    * signup -> call signup callback
    * login -> login callback
2. After doing this logic, return [SUCCESS, FAILED]
3. Create an auth post route with the same three parameters
4. call the function
    * if success -> redirect
    * if failed -> alert

html -> POST /auth -> auth.js -> SUCCESS or FAILED -> /auth -> html -> redirect or not?